comments: Marshall (NOP) cleanly dislodges the ball from Markkanen (UTA) during his drive toward the rim.
Olynyk (UTA) jumps forward and initiates body contact with Jones (NOP) during his driving shot attempt.
Olynyk (UTA) firms up in McCollum's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as McCollum is moving through the pick.
McCollum (NOP) firms up in Markkanen's (UTA) path and the contact during the screen is marginal.
Clarkson (UTA) and Jones (NOP) come together and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Olynyk (UTA) taps the ball out of Jones' (NOP) hand during the rebound attempt.
Nance Jr. (NOP) and Olynyk (UTA) come together and incidental contact occurs as both players dive for the loose ball.
McCollum's (NOP) hand slides off Olynyk's (UTA) body as he is moving underneath the pick.
Kessler (UTA) and Nance Jr. (NOP) mutually engage as the shot goes up. As they are disengaging Kessler slightly extends his arm into Nance Jr.
Williamson (NOP) drives towards Olynyk's (UTA) space, but does not dislodge him from his defensive position.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Graham (NOP) and Conley (UTA) come together and mutually engage and disengage as Graham is running through the lane.
Olynyk (UTA) briefly grasps Nance Jr.'s (NOP) arm during the rebound attempt.
Nance Jr. (NOP) makes incidental contact with Clarkson (UTA) as Nance Jr. is falling to the floor.
Valanciunas (NOP) extends his leg out and makes intentional foot to ball contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a goaltending on Nance Jr. (NOP) is overturned and no basket is scored.
Olynyk (UTA) and Nance Jr. (NOP) come together and marginal contact occurs as Olynyk is moving through the pick.
Olynyk (UTA) briefly clamps Williamson's (NOP) arm as he is running through the lane.
McCollum (NOP) moves alongside Olynyk (UTA) path and the contact during the shot attempt is marginal.
Olynyk (UTA) hand slides off Nance Jr.'s (NOP) side and the contact during the pick is marginal.
Kessler (UTA) moves alongside Williamson's (NOP) path and maintains a legal vertical position while contesting the shot attempt.
Nance Jr. (NOP) and Kessler (UTA) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Williamson (NOP) initiates more than marginal contact with Conley (UTA) during his drive toward the rim.
Replay review of the foul called on Nance Jr. (NOP) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Nance Jr. initiates more than marginal body contact with Kessler.
Olynyk (UTA) absorbs the contact initiated by Williamson (NOP) and the contact during the shot attempt is marginal.
Murphy III (NOP) initiates contact with Conley's (UTA) body as he is dribbling the ball up the floor.
Conley (UTA) cleanly dislodges the ball from McCollum (NOP).
Nance Jr. (NOP) and Kessler (UTA) mutually clamp each other as both players go for the loose ball.
Nance Jr. (NOP) commits a take foul on Markkanen (UTA). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
